[1.03 beta 1]
This is the distributed installation initialize version.
Include:
Hadoop Install
LZO compression libary
JDK 7u5
It can do:
1. Installing Hadoop, Lzo compression libary, Jdk with fast socket pushing agent.
2. Setting up Hadoop-settings and push them to nodes you wished(like hdfs-site.xml).
3. Setting up Common-settings and push them to each node(like /etc/hosts)
4. Manage hadoop setup files for each nodes.
5. Monitoring hadoop process health status, and renturn the processId on nodes
6. Start, stop, restart namenode, jobtracker... for each node with one click.
7. View hadoop logs within 1000 lines
8. EHM user management